{
  "name": "config-cascade-variants",
  "createdAt": "2026-05-18T08:25:29.069Z",
  "description": "Add layered config cascade for specd.yaml variants with standalone local fallback. Introduces extends (true and explicit path), remove directives, deep merge semantics, and ordered candidate discovery (specd.yaml → specd.*.yaml → specd.local.yaml → specd.local.*.yaml). Backward-compatible: specd.local.yaml without extends remains a standalone replacement.",
